      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DENNIS KEEPING (3) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (29.64) at this track behind Royal Bandit in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Rates highly and will give a great sight. SABINI (2) scored well last start as odds-on favourite by 0.8 lengths at Bulli in a handy 22.69 beating Twisted Huxley. Draws to advantage and goes well over this trip. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Sure to be thereabouts. ELLE'S MOON (1) ran a handy 29.88 when filling a minor placing over 520m at this track last start. Has the ability and can measure up. NATISA'S SECRET (8) missed the frame latest (30.31) when sixth over 520m at this track in a Grade 4/5. Already a winner from this draw.",
